description: This file contains C header declarations for interacting with RBus API related to WAN connectivity checks, including function prototypes for initialization, registration, unregistration, feature commit, interface commit, URL commit, and URL deletion.

methods.name: CosaWanCnctvtyChk_RbusInit
methods.description: Initializes the RBus connection for WAN connectivity checking.

methods.name: CosaWanCnctvtyChk_Reg_elements
methods.description: Registers elements of a specified DML type with RBus for WAN connectivity checking.

methods.name: CosaWanCnctvtyChk_UnReg_elements
methods.description: Unregisters elements of a specified DML type from RBus for WAN connectivity checking.

methods.name: CosaWanCnctvtyChk_Feature_Commit
methods.description: Commits or applies the feature enable/disable setting for WAN connectivity check.

methods.name: CosaWanCnctvtyChk_Intf_Commit
methods.description: Commits the configuration of a specific WAN interface for connectivity checking.

methods.name: CosaWanCnctvtyChk_URL_Commit
methods.description: Commits or updates a URL configuration for a specific InstanceNumber.

methods.name: CosaWanCnctvtyChk_URL_delDBEntry
methods.description: Deletes a URL entry from the database for a specific InstanceNumber.

calls: rbus/rbus.h (used for rbusError_t type and related functions)
cosa_wanconnectivity_apis.h (defines related data structures and types)
